The offsets of almost all fields after iTOW are different due to these structural changes. The manual explicitly states support for M8 protocol versions 20, 20.01, etc., up to 23.01. The canonical definition appears to correspond to a later protocol version, likely from the F9 series, despite listing '1800' as a supported protocol version.
